These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
Flower: aconite, sunflower, orchid, daffodil
Pet: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
Birthday: december, may, april, july
1. Birthday:april is on the left of Pet:ferret##1
2. Birthday:july == Pet:cat##1
3. Flower:orchid is on the far left##1
4. Flower:aconite is on the far right##1
5. Pet:ferret is between Birthday:april and Flower:sunflower##2
6. Birthday:may == Pet:lizard##1
7. Pet:cat is on the right of Pet:ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Flower        | orchid | daffodil  | sunflower | aconite  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Birthday   | april     | december | july       | may |

