1. Hobby:drawing is on the far left##1
2. City:nizza is on the right of Hobby:chess##1
3. City:san-francisco is on the far left##1
4. City:rome is between House:craftsman and Hobby:reading##2
5. House:craftsman == City:san-francisco##1
6. House:ranch-style is on the left of City:nizza##1
7. House:palace == City:marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| House   | craftsman  | ranch-style  | victorian   | palace    |
| City         | san-francisco | rome | nizza | marseilles      |

